      "text": "About the Section"
    },
    {
      "id": "n2",
      "type": "image",
      "order": 1,
      "src": "https://deutsch-pruefung.de/_next/image?url=%2Fsection-assets%2Fbear-mascot.webp&w=384&q=75",
      "alt": "Study bear mascot"
    },
    {
      "id": "n3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 2,
      "text": "The Goethe B1 Reading module has five parts. You will read several texts and complete tasks related to them."
    },
    {
      "id": "n4",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 3,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 1: Reading Correspondence"
    },
    {
      "id": "n5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 4,
      "text": "• Goal: understand personal or professional correspondence (emails, letters, forum posts)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 5,
      "text": "• Task: judge six statements as true or false based on the text"
    },
    {
      "id": "n7",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 6,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 2: Understanding Information & Arguments"
    },
    {
      "id": "n8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 7,
      "text": "• Goal: analyse an informational article and grasp the author’s line of argumentation"
    },
    {
      "id": "n9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 8,
      "text": "• Task: choose the correct answer from three options for each prompt"
    },
    {
      "id": "n10",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 9,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 3: Reading for Orientation"
    },
    {
      "id": "n11",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 10,
      "text": "• Goal: orient yourself quickly in notices, adverts, or short descriptions"
    },
    {
      "id": "n12",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 11,
      "text": "• Task: match seven short profiles or situations to the best-fitting text; one option will remain unused"
    },
    {
      "id": "n13",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 12,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 4: Opinions & Arguments"
    },
    {
      "id": "n14",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 13,
      "text": "• Goal: understand viewpoints and supporting arguments in reader comments or opinion snippets"
    },
    {
      "id": "n15",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 14,
      "text": "• Task: decide for each statement whether it agrees with the text (Yes/No)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n16",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 15,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 5: Understanding Written Instructions"
    },
    {
      "id": "n17",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 16,
      "text": "• Goal: extract rules or instructions from formal texts such as house regulations or guidelines"
    },
    {
      "id": "n18",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 17,
      "text": "• Task: pick the correct statement from three options for each prompt"
    },
    {
